instruction: Suggest a meal that can be prepared in less than 30 minutes.
output: A quick and easy meal that can be prepared in less than 30 minutes is a simple garlic-buttered shrimp pasta. Start by sautéing garlic in olive oil for a few minutes before adding in peeled and deveined shrimp. Cook the shrimp for a few minutes before adding in cooked pasta, Alfredo sauce and freshly grated Parmesan cheese. Mix everything together and you'll have a delicious and simple meal ready in no time.
